    public class ActionBatch
extends LinkedBlockingQueue<CheckedConsumer<org.apache.sling.api.resource.ResourceResolver>>
    Manage a queue of actions that are processed and committed in batches. The number of actions processed in a batch is determined by the size of the queue.
